    function setCookie(a, b, c) { 
        var d = new Date;
        d.setTime(d.getTime() + 24 * c * 60 * 60 * 1e3);
        var e = "expires=" + d.toUTCString();
        document.cookie = a + "=" + b + "; " + e + "; path=/"

	function viewMoreCityContent(){
$("#contentsPart1").css('overflow-y','visible');
$("#contentsPart1").css('height','auto');
$("#contentVewMore").hide();
$("#contentVewLess").css('display','block');

function viewLessCityContent(){

$("#contentsPart1").css('height','185px');
$("#contentVewLess").hide();
$("#contentVewMore").show();

var x = 7; //number of cards to be displayed
showOnly(document.querySelectorAll("#timeline t"),x);
showOnly(document.querySelectorAll("#timeline1 t"),x);
function showOnly(nodeList, index) {
     for (i = 0; i < nodeList.length; i++ ) {
       nodeList[i].style.display = i<index ? "block": "none";
     }
}

function addLoadEvent(recall) {
  var oldonload = window.onload;
  if (typeof window.onload != 'function') {
    window.onload = recall;
  } else {
    window.onload = function() {
      oldonload();
      recall();
    };
  }
}

document.getElementById('body').addEventListener('mousemove', function() {
	cb();
},{ once: true }
